<br>
I am sick of being sent home from work because of Bomb Threats in the skyscraper I work in or nearby skyscrapers. <br>
<br>
I can't think of a single instance of a bomb threat accomplishing anything other than to further separate the threatening organization from the sypathies of the rest of the world.<br>
<br>
I can't think of a single act of terrorism that has earned any organization the respect of the world.<br>
<br>
Actually I can't think of a single act of terrorism that actually produced terror that lasted more than a few a weeks. The physical damage done by terrorists will last a long time but when we see it and remember we wont remember fear, we will remember anger and resolve.<br>
<br>
Terrorism does not work. It never has it never will. These dumb train jumping nuts...<br>
<br>
Anyway, it needs to stop.<br>
<br>
